---
import Layout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Orbete — Ton programme d'accompagnement Be-Cosmo"
  description="Orbete t'aide à structurer, développer et ancrer ton activité — depuis ton lieu Be-Cosmo."
>
  <!-- ═══ HERO V3 ═══ -->
  <section class="hero-v3-signature">
    <div class="hero-glow-layer">
      <div class="glow-red"></div>
      <div class="glow-green"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="container hero-container text-center">
      <div class="hero-header">
        <div class="top-nav-v3">
          <a href="/a-propos">À propos</a>
          <a href="/ressources">Ressources</a>
          <a href="/diagnostic">Diagnostic</a>
          <a href="/copilote" class="desktop-copilot-link">Copilote</a>
          <a href="/login" class="nav-login-btn">Se connecter</a>
        </div>
        <span class="hero-badge">Programme Be-Cosmo</span>
        <div class="hero-brand-wrap">
          <span class="brand-logo-full">Orbete</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1>Ton programme d'accompagnement.<br /><span class="emphasis">Gratuit. À ton rythme.</span></h1>
        <p class="hero-lead">
          Orbete t'aide à structurer, développer et ancrer ton activité<br />
          — depuis ton lieu Be-Cosmo.
        </p>

        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="/diagnostic" class="btn-primary-v3 big pulse-border">Commencer mon diagnostic →</a>
          <a href="/ressources" class="btn-secondary-v3 hero-secondary">Découvrir les ressources</a>
          <div class="hero-hint">
            <span class="dot-neon"></span> Gratuit · Confidentiel · À ton rythme
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-footer-line">
      <span class="dash-neon"></span>
      <span class="dash-red"></span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ BLOC DIFFÉRENCE ═══ -->
  <section class="section-v3 bg-light">
    <div class="container container-medium">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="label-v3">Différenciation</span>
        <h2>Ce n'est pas une IA <span class="emphasis">qui répond.</span></h2>
        <p class="intro-v3">
          C'est un outil pour ne pas décider seul.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="diff-grid-v3">
        <div class="diff-block card-v3 highlight-neon">
          <p class="diff-quote" style="font-size:1.4rem; margin-bottom:1.5rem; color:var(--deep);">
            Ce n’est pas une IA qui répond.<br />
            C’est un appui pour ne pas décider seul·e.
          </p>
          <p class="secondary" style="opacity:0.8; font-size:1.1rem; line-height:1.6;">
            Orbete ne donne pas des réponses toutes faites. 
            Elle vous aide à comprendre ce que vous vivez, à poser les bonnes questions, 
            et à éviter de réagir trop vite.
          </p>
          <p class="secondary" style="margin-top:1.5rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--accent-red);">
            Et quand c’est nécessaire, elle vous rappelle une chose simple : 
            <strong>aller parler avec les gens.</strong>
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="diff-block card-v3">
          <span class="label-v3">Une autre manière de travailler</span>
          <p style="font-size:1.15rem; margin-bottom:1rem; font-weight:700;">Décider vite ne veut pas dire décider seul.</p>
          <p style="opacity:0.8; font-size:0.95rem;">
            Dans beaucoup de situations, ce n’est pas une réponse qu’il manque, 
            c’est un peu de recul, un bon cadrage, 
            et parfois une conversation au bon endroit.
          </p>
          <a href="/diagnostic" class="btn-primary-v3" style="margin-top:2rem; width:100%;">Faire le diagnostic</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ BLOC POLITIQUE ═══ -->
  <section class="section-v3 bg-deep text-white">
    <div class="glow-v3 glow-red" style="top:-20%;left:-10%;"></div>
    <div class="container container-medium text-center" style="position:relative;z-index:2;">
      <span class="label-v3">Une autre façon de faire de la activité</span>
      <h2 class="text-white" style="font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem); margin: 2rem 0;">
        Pas plus lente.<br />
        Pas plus compliquée.<br />
        Juste plus <span class="emphasis">lucide.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="intro-v3 text-white" style="opacity:0.75; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 4rem;">
        Prendre deux minutes pour cadrer une situation,<br />
        c'est parfois éviter deux semaines de rattrapage.
      </p>
      <a href="/diagnostic" class="btn-primary-v3 big">Démarrer maintenant</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ BLOC METHODE ═══ -->
  <section class="section-v3">
    <div class="container container-medium">
      <div class="section-header text-center">
        <span class="label-v3">La Méthode</span>
        <h2>Un appui en <span class="emphasis">trois temps</span></h2>
      </div>

      <div class="method-steps">
        <a href="/diagnostic" class="step-v3 step-link-v3">
          <div class="step-num">01.</div>
          <h3>Diagnostic initial</h3>
          <p>5 minutes pour qualifier votre profil et vos besoins prioritaires.</p>
        </a>
        <div class="step-arrow-v3"></div>
        <a href="/copilote" class="step-v3 step-link-v3">
          <div class="step-num">02.</div>
          <h3>Appui Copilote</h3>
          <p>Accès immédiat à l'agent de discernement et aux ressources ciblées.</p>
        </a>
        <div class="step-arrow-v3"></div>
        <a href="/hub-experts" class="step-v3 step-link-v3">
          <div class="step-num">03.</div>
          <h3>Hub d'Experts</h3>
          <p>Passage de relais à nos experts humains sur les arbitrages critiques.</p>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="method-actions">
        <a href="/diagnostic" class="btn-primary-v3">Faire le diagnostic</a>
        <a href="/copilote" class="btn-secondary-v3">Tester le copilote gratuit</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ BLOC HUMAIN ═══ -->
  <section class="section-v3 bg-deep dark-hub">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hub-v3-inner">
        <div class="hub-v3-content">
          <span class="label-v3">Le Réseau</span>
          <h2 class="text-white">Un outil. Et un <span class="emphasis">relais humain</span><br />quand il le faut.</h2>
          <p style="font-size:1.25rem;color:white;opacity:0.95;margin-bottom:1rem;">
            Parce que certaines situations ne se traitent pas seul.
          </p>
          <p style="font-size:1rem;color:white;opacity:0.75;max-width:500px;margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
            Orbete vous aide à savoir quand continuer… et quand vous entourer. 
            Notre réseau de consultants (Stratégie, Droit, Communication, RH) prend le relais sur les dossiers les plus sensibles.
          </p>
          <a href="/hub-experts" class="btn-secondary-v3">Explorer les expertises</a>
        </div>
        <div class="hub-v3-badge">
          <div class="hub-badge-circle">
            <span>Hybridation <br /><b>Humaine</b></span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ FINAL CTA ═══ -->
  <section class="section-v3 bg-ivory final-cta-section">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <div class="final-box-v3">
        <span class="label-v3">Prêt à naviguer ?</span>
        <h2>Reprenez de la <span class="emphasis">clarté</span><br />sur votre projet.</h2>
        <div class="final-actions-v3">
          <a href="/diagnostic" class="btn-primary-v3 big">Faire le diagnostic (5min)</a>
          <a href="/copilote" class="btn-secondary-v3 big">Tester le copilote gratuit</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-link-simple">Poser une question à l'équipe</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    /* ─── NAVIGATION ─── */
    .top-nav-v3 {
      display: flex; gap: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 2.5rem); justify-content: center; 
      margin-bottom: 3.5rem; opacity: 0.6; padding-top: 1rem;
    }
    .top-nav-v3 a { 
      color: white; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; 
      text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; transition: all 0.2s; 
    }
    .top-nav-v3 a:hover { color: white; opacity: 1; }
    .nav-login-btn {
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.35) !important;
      padding: 0.35rem 0.9rem !important;
      border-radius: 99px !important;
      opacity: 1 !important;
    }
    .nav-login-btn:hover { border-color: white !important; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); }
    .desktop-copilot-link,
    .desktop-copilot-cta { display: inline-flex; }

    /* ─── HERO V3 ─── */
    .hero-v3-signature {
      position: relative;
      background-color: var(--deep);
      padding: 8rem 0 10rem;
      color: white;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--neon);
    }
    .hero-glow-layer { position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 0; pointer-events: none; }
    .glow-red { position: absolute; top: 10%; left: 0%; width: 50vw; height: 50vw; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.08) 0%, transparent 70%); }
    .glow-green { position: absolute; bottom: 10%; right: 0%; width: 40vw; height: 40vw; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(173, 255, 47, 0.05) 0%, transparent 70%); }
    .hero-container { position: relative; z-index: 2; margin-top: -1rem; }
    .hero-header { margin-bottom: 4rem; position: relative; z-index: 10; }

    .hero-badge { display: inline-block; padding: 0.65rem 1.5rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 99px; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.05em; color: white; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }

    .hero-brand-wrap { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
    .brand-logo-full {
      font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 15vw, 9rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #FFFFFF 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.7) 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      display: block;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .hero-v3-signature h1 { font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 4rem); color: white; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 1.1; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
    .hero-lead { font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.35rem); line-height: 1.7; opacity: 0.8; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 3.5rem; }
    .text-neon { color: var(--neon); }
    .text-red { color: var(--accent-red); }

    .hero-actions { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 1.5rem; }
    .hero-alt-entry {
      margin: -0.1rem 0 0;
      max-width: 34rem;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
    }
    .hero-secondary {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      color: white;
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
    }
    .hero-secondary:hover {
      background: white;
      color: var(--deep);
      border-color: white;
    }
    .pulse-border { position: relative; }
    .pulse-border::after { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: -3px; border-radius: 99px; border: 1.5px solid var(--neon); opacity: 0.3; animation: pulse 2s infinite; }
    @keyframes pulse { 0% { scale: 1; opacity: 0.5; } 100% { scale: 1.1; opacity: 0; } }

    .hero-hint { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.5; font-weight: 600; }
    .dot-neon { width: 8px; height: 8px; background: var(--neon); border-radius: 50%; box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--neon); }
    .hero-footer-line { position: absolute; bottom: 3rem; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); display: flex; gap: 2rem; }
    .dash-neon { width: 60px; height: 1.5px; background: var(--neon); border-radius: 99px; opacity: 0.5; }
    .dash-red { width: 60px; height: 1.5px; background: var(--accent-red); border-radius: 99px; opacity: 0.5; }

    /* ─── DIFF GRID ─── */
    .diff-grid-v3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; margin-top: 4rem; }
    .diff-block { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; }
    .diff-quote { font-family: var(--font-accent); font-style: italic; font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--deep); line-height: 1.3; }
    .diff-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }
    .diff-list li { padding: 0.75rem 1rem; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.03); border-radius: 12px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .highlight-neon { border-color: var(--neon); border-width: 2px; }

    /* ─── METHOD ─── */
    .method-steps { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 2rem; margin: 4rem 0; }
    .step-v3 { flex: 1; }
    .step-link-v3 {
      display: block;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 24px;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease;
    }
    .step-link-v3:hover,
    .step-link-v3:focus-visible {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      border-color: var(--border);
      background: white;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 28px rgba(10, 25, 47, 0.06);
      outline: none;
    }
    .step-num { font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--deep); opacity: 0.1; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .step-v3 h3 { margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.2rem; }
    .step-arrow-v3 { width: 40px; height: 1.5px; background: var(--border); margin-top: 5rem; }
    .method-actions {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
    }

    /* ─── HUB ─── */
    .dark-hub { border-radius: 60px 60px 0 0; margin-top: -2rem; }
    .hub-v3-inner { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5rem; }
    .hub-v3-content { flex: 1; }
    .hub-v3-content h2 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .hub-v3-badge { flex-shrink: 0; }
    .hub-badge-circle { width: 160px; height: 160px; border: 1px solid var(--neon); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-align: center; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.3; }
    .hub-badge-circle b { color: var(--neon); text-transform: uppercase; }

    /* ─── FINAL CTA ─── */
    .bg-ivory { background-color: #FDFBFA; }
    .final-box-v3 { padding: 4rem 2rem; }
    .final-box-v3 h2 { font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem); line-height: 1.1; margin: 2rem 0 3.5rem; }
    .final-actions-v3 { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 1.5rem; }
    .btn-link-simple { font-weight: 700; color: #54636C; text-decoration: underline; }

    /* ─── RESPONSIVE ─── */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero-v3-signature { padding: 6rem 1.5rem 8rem; }
      .method-steps { flex-direction: column; gap: 3rem; }
      .step-arrow-v3 { display: none; }
      .hub-v3-inner { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; gap: 3rem; }
      .hub-v3-badge { order: -1; }
      .diff-grid-v3 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .desktop-only { display: none; }
      .method-actions { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; }
      .method-actions a,
      .final-actions-v3 a,
      .hero-actions a { width: 100%; }
    }

    .text-center { text-align: center !important; }
    .bg-deep { background: var(--deep); }
    .bg-light { background: var(--bg); }
    .text-white { color: white !important; }
    .container-medium { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .overflow-hidden { overflow: hidden; }
  </style>
</Layout>
